## stmt 内 outer join 谓词推导以及push down 测试
EXPLAIN select t1.c3, t2.c3, t3.c3 from (t1 left join t2 on t1.c1 = t2.c1) left join t3 on t1.c1 = t3.c1 where t1.c1 = 1;
